 justify;\">Je suis vraiment désolé pour les périodes creuses, et j\'espère que ce petit souci sera vite réglé.</div><br /><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Je ne vous laisse pas attendre plus longtemps, vous avez déjà assez attendu n\'est-ce pas ? ^^</div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://kichigai-fansub.blogspot.be/2014/07/oyaji-no-senaka.html\"><b><span style=\"color: #990000;\">Oyajo no Senaka 05</span></b></a></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #990000;\"><i><b>Mao.</b></i></span></div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"http://kichigai-fansub.blogspot.com/2014/11/oyaji-no-senaka-05.html\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"noreply@blogger.com (Mao Chi)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:7:\"updated\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"2014-11-27T21:28:33.125+01:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"url\";s:149:\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-QzX3jDyGqz4/VHd86hg4MgI/AAAAAAAAAvs/NNnkTRamih8/s72-c/Capture%2Bd%E2%80%99e%CC%81cran%2B2014-11-27%2Ba%CC%80%2B20.30.20.png\";s:6:\"height\";s:2:\"72\";s:5:\"width\";s:2:\"72\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0\";a:1:{s:5:\"total\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attrib