lor: #990000;\">pèlerinages japonais</span></b>, c\'est sympa en tout cas : )</div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Je fais cette news vite fait entre deux travaux donc je vous dis déjà à la semaine prochaine pour la suite : )</div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://kichigai-fansub.blogspot.be/2014/07/oyaji-no-senaka.html\"><b><span style=\"color: #990000;\">Oyaji no Senaka 04</span></b></a></div><br /><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><i><b><span style=\"color: #990000;\">Bonne soirée !</span></b></i></div><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><i><b><span style=\"color: #990000;\">Mao.</span></b></i></div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"http://kichigai-fansub.blogspot.com/2014/11/oyaji-no-senaka-04.html\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"noreply@blogger.com (Mao Chi)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:7:\"updated\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"2014-11-06T22:41:37.108+01:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"url\";s:149:\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-h88nxHCNer8/VFuXe4Q2dgI/AAAAAAAAAvU/JjrEvpxYzrI/s72-c/Capture%2Bd%E2%80%99e%CC%81cran%2B2014-11-06%2Ba%CC%80%2B16.41.55.png\";s:6:\"height\";s:2:\"72\";s:5:\"width\";s:2:\"72\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0\";a:1:{s:5:\"total\";a:1:{i:0