"color: #990000;\">Cupcake</span></b> mais vous n\'y verrez que du feu puisque les épisodes continueront à sortir normalement.</div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Enfin voilà, je vous laisse découvrir ce nouveau drama, en espérant qu\'il vous plaise malgré un casting moins connu, en tout cas, moi j\'ai adoré ! ; )</div><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://kichigai-fansub.blogspot.be/2014/01/fukuie-keibuho-no-aisatsu.html\"><b><span style=\"color: #990000;\">Fukuie 01</span></b></a></div><br />Bonne soirée à tous,<br /><br /><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><b><i><span style=\"color: #990000;\">La Kichigai-Fansub.</span></i></b></div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"http://kichigai-fansub.blogspot.com/2014/05/fukuie-keibuho-no-aisatsu-01.html\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"noreply@blogger.com (Mao Chi)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:7:\"updated\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"2014-05-30T00:56:42.924+02:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"url\";s:141:\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-k1GIP2tvySU/U4e0D-F9jII/AAAAAAAAAdk/FZRyTQWU09U/s72-c/Capture+d%E2%80%99e%CC%81cran+2014-05-30+a%CC%80+00.16.43.png\";s:6:\"height\";s:2:\"72\";s:5:\"width\";s:2:\"72\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0\";a:1:{s:5:\"total\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s: